channel.title: Scripts just don't seem to progress or even click
channel.description:
I used scar years ago with ease but now it seems it just wont function?! I've tried using stupid3ooo's power miner like I did before, it hovers over the ore, say it's found colors, does not click. Sum's power miner does pretty much the same thing, as well as starblasters?
I have the includes and the script runs but almost nothing happens? I'm using firefox, also tried I.E my color is on 32bit high?
My screen refresh rate is 60hertz, could that be it?
WTF AM I DOING WRONG?!
